                                                                                                                              </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>New Delhi: <a href=\"/tag/molbio+diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Molbio Diagnostics</a> announced that its subsidiary <a href=\"/tag/prognosys+medical+systems\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Prognosys Medical Systems</a> has secured the European Union Quality Management System certification under Regulation (EU) 2017/745 (EU MDR) for its <a href=\"/tag/medical+imaging+portfolio\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medical imaging portfolio</a>.The certification, issued by TÜV SÜD Product Service GmbH, marks company to expand into globally regulated markets and reflects its adherence to international standards for safety, quality, and clinical performance.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><a href=\"/tag/prognosys+medical+systems\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Prognosys Medical Systems</a> develops digital imaging solutions, including fixed and mobile platforms aimed at improving diagnostic access across diverse healthcare settings. The development supports Molbio’s integrated diagnostics strategy by combining molecular diagnostics with radiological imaging to enable faster and more decentralised disease detection.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        According to the company, the certification indicates that the ProRad portfolio meets international quality and regulatory standards required for deployment across global healthcare programs.“This certification is not only significant for Molbio but also reflects the growing capability of Indian medtech innovation. The milestone demonstrates the potential of ‘Make in India’ solutions in global med-tech markets.,” said Sriram Natarajan, Executive Director and CEO, <a href=\"/tag/molbio+diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Molbio Diagnostics</a>.                    \n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Apr 1, 2026 at 03:20 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Apr 1, 2026 at 03:20 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-app-store.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                        </div>    -->\n      